<item>
            <title>[LU-15498] WBC: reint create under WBC should return layout EA</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15498</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Normal reint creation (@ll_new_node) will not return layout EA (lov EA) to the client.&lt;br/&gt;
However, a regular file under WBC needs the layout EA to assimilate the cache pages during flush,  thus it needs to return layout EA for it.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
